{"tid":2271351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"由朝早8點睇到而家，臨尾同我Trump輸，我依家真係好想喊","createTime":"2020-11-04T13:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T18:15:23.000Z","uid":43785,"like":603,"dislike":111,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"5e99dfe9806282cd39f63727411069ce9f4c7fb8","tid":2271351,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T13:30:25.000Z","msg":"由朝早8點睇到而家，你同我Trump輸，我依家真係好想喊。<br />\n<br />\n好老實，今日美國大選，仲緊張過上年過區選。<br />\n無時無刻都睇住啲票，由冇希望變到有希望，下晝嘅時候，我真係一度以為Trump會贏。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點會諗到，來到呢一刻我哋會輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係有啲接受唔到，眼淚不停喺眼角流出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n我真係寧願一輸就輸鳩曬，好過畀曬希望大家然後一鋪清袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講笑都要講一句，冇諗過大家真係燈力咁犀利，叫撚咗大家唔好亂開香檳，講真話仲要BLOCK鳩我，依家仆街啦。屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我今日真係有一刻覺得trump會贏。<br />\n可惜只係一場夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想喊<br />\n好想呢個世界有奇蹟...<br />\n好想.....好想睇多四年trump<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌，今鋪真係乜都冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人同我一樣都係好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77fffec6a9a91bcb5a571e7859b57ce5214298e","tid":2271351,"uid":38737,"like":97,"dislike":43,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T13:30:45.000Z","msg":"你點喊的"},{"pid":"f1b13aebe625d568275a255fb086e028fc86e985","tid":2271351,"uid":102926,"like":29,"dislike":16,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T13:30:47.000Z","msg":"你點知的"},{"pid":"c2c13fc7813fe12e243077b621333ba887646c7d","tid":2271351,"uid":312